
Installation of the Mapbox Navigation SDK for iOS
->Create an Ios App in Xcode, named Mapbox_demo on the Desktop
-> In the console cd Destop > cd Mapbox_demo : sudo gem install cocoapods
=> Create in the folder Mapbox_demo -> Creation of a file name PodFile
-> Open PodFile in Atom and paste pod 'MapboxNavigation', '~> 0.16'
# Pods for Mapbox_demo
  pod 'MapboxNavigation', '~> 0.16'
-> Open the console In the console cd Destop > cd Mapbox_demo : pod repo update && pod install
=> Downloading dependencies
Installing Mapbox-iOS-SDK (3.7.6)
Installing MapboxCoreNavigation (0.16.2)
Installing MapboxDirections.swift (0.19.1)
Installing MapboxMobileEvents (0.4.0)
Installing MapboxNavigation (0.16.2)
Installing MapboxSpeech (0.0.1)
Installing Polyline (4.2.0)
Installing Solar (2.1.0)
Installing Turf (0.1.1)
Generating Pods project
